{"tid":1087162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有圖】腳蹺儀表板追求舒服　慘烈代價！她失去額頭2年","createTime":"2019-04-01T07:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T17:16:46.000Z","uid":130626,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1d6285573f7d2ef2d72646dfbca0dec6c503f64a","tid":1087162,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T07:43:08.000Z","msg":"有些人搭車時將腳蹺到儀表板上，愛爾蘭萊伊什郡一名35歲的女生凱莉（Grainne Kealy）用自己的血淚經驗奉勸你不要這麼做。原來凱莉在22歲搭男友的車時，因為想讓自己舒服一點，而將腳蹺到儀表板上，結果發生車禍時安全氣囊的巨大威力讓她的膝蓋往自己臉狠狠砸下，她除了傷痕更因此過了2年沒有前額的悲慘生活。<br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，2007年12月時，凱莉男友的吉普車因為道路結冰打滑而撞牆，安全氣囊瞬間以時速200英里（約322公里）統氣彈出，結果凱莉的雙腳膝蓋因為放在儀表板的關係，被震開往自己臉上猛砸，凱莉臉部骨折、丟了兩顆牙齒、部分腦脊液漏出，她花了很長的時間來恢復。想不到之後凱莉的前額不斷萎縮，最後不得不動手術將整個前額骨取出，就此凱莉開始了「失去額頭」的生活。<br />\n凱莉的額頭詭異地塌陷，讓她很長一段時間拒絕出門，不願和朋友接觸，甚至連站在鏡子前面的勇氣都沒有，不過她的家人和男友並沒有放棄，花了大約2年的時間，凱莉才從義大利尋找到可以替代的陶瓷人造前額骨，經過整形手術後，凱莉終於恢復了正常的面貌。<br />\n凱莉有感於像賽琳娜（Selena Gomez）這些明星，經常在社群網站分享將腳蹺在儀表板上的照片，批評她們在傳遞錯誤訊息給數億粉絲，她希望用自己的切身之痛來警告大家，「我希望大家傾聽並從我糟糕的經歷中學到教訓，因為它真的是一條困難的道路，而且我還持續在這條路上」，凱莉表示，儘管外觀已經恢復，但她頭部的創傷其實還沒有完全復原，她有時在談話過程中會突然失語，另外也相當容易頭痛。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190401/640_a8010717733aa6b039d675f172720220.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190401%2F640_a8010717733aa6b039d675f172720220.jpg&h=4e880a60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190401/640_82d8af4a538fa3401663fd4faa53c45e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190401%2F640_82d8af4a538fa3401663fd4faa53c45e.jpg&h=c0a4e62f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190401/640_387de2c6f2e69051e85ce7475fc85e1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190401%2F640_387de2c6f2e69051e85ce7475fc85e1c.jpg&h=79be3568&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190401/640_e02e468fa852019553653aa0a452f9b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190401%2F640_e02e468fa852019553653aa0a452f9b3.jpg&h=9745c20d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190401/640_bb079829f778049465abbd15b1e5aa88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190401%2F640_bb079829f778049465abbd15b1e5aa88.jpg&h=42028664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190401/1543159/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190401%2F1543159%2F&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQixR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=d237e5c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190401%2F1543159%2F&h=50f80399\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190401/1543159/</a>"},{"pid":"39ceef3a310e758904039e1c19b8b520c46f6873","tid":1087162,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T07:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd885732f2a0055eb2f4ad91422627132a5cd46","tid":1087162,"uid":4574,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T07:59:43.000Z","msg":"可以擺嘢 幾方便"},{"pid":"e5fab3af72b0630a149c6b5c5dccb8ae20355060","tid":1087162,"uid":220431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ebd885732f2a0055eb2f4ad91422627132a5cd46","tid":1087162,"uid":4574,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T07:59:43.000Z","msg":"可以擺嘢 幾方便"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T08:02:19.000Z","msg":"擺下遮咁"},{"pid":"3844474a425f9de2392b9d4aa85c16e7b080eab6","tid":1087162,"uid":89514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T08:32:22.000Z","msg":"此